<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Nature Stay Sigiriya - Homestay in Sri Lanka</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Nature Stay Sigiriya</h1>
            <p>Your Peaceful Home Near the Ancient Rock Fortress</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container content">
        
        <!-- About Section -->
        <section class="about">
            <h2>Welcome to Our Homestay</h2>
            <p>Experience authentic Sri Lankan hospitality just minutes away from the famous Sigiriya Rock. We offer comfortable rooms, delicious home-cooked traditional meals, and a peaceful environment surrounded by nature.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Features Section -->
        <section class="features">
            <h2>What We Offer</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Comfortable Rooms:</strong> Clean beds, A/C or fan, and private bathrooms.</li>
                <li><strong>Free Wi-Fi:</strong> Stay connected with high-speed internet.</li>
                <li><strong>Authentic Food:</strong> Enjoy fresh, homemade Sri Lankan rice and curry.</li>
                <li><strong>Great Location:</strong> Easy access to Sigiriya Rock, Pidurangala, and wildlife safaris.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact & Booking Section -->
        <section class="contact">
            <h2>Book Your Stay</h2>
            <p>Ready to visit? Contact us directly for the best rates!</p>
            <p><strong>📞 Phone / WhatsApp:</strong> +94 717388681</p>
            <p><strong>✉️ Email:</strong>Nikinihomestay@gmail.com</p>
            <p><strong>📍 Location:</strong> Sigiriya, Sri Lanka</p>
        </section>

    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Nature Stay Sigiriya. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
/* General Styles */
body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    color: #333;
}

.container {
    width: 85%;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: auto;
    overflow: hidden;
}

/* Header */
header {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586861635167-e5223aadc9fe?q=80&w=1200') no-repeat center center/cover;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 80px 0;
    text-align: center;
}

header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
}

header p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
}

/* Content Sections */
.content {
    padding: 20px 0;
}

section {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 30px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
}

h2 {
    color: #2c5e3b; /* Nature Green */
    border-bottom: 2px solid #2c5e3b;
    padding-bottom: 5px;
}

ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
}

ul li {
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
}

/* Footer */
footer {
    background: #2c5e3b;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 15px 0;
    margin-top: 40px;
}
